%C A396541 \                    |    |    |    |         |    |           |     |
%C A396541  \  tau() = n        |  1 |  2 |  3 |    4    |  5 |    6      |  7  |
%C A396541   ---------------    |    |    |    |         |    |           |     |
%C A396541              in  \   |    |    |    |         |    |           |     |
%C A396541 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
%C A396541  [        1..2^(n-1)]| 2^0| 2^1| 2^2|  6.. 2^3| 2^4|   12.. 2^5| 2^6 | A005179..A000079
%C A396541  [2^(n-1)+1..3^(n-1)]| 3^0| 3^1| 3^2| 10.. 3^3| 3^4|   44.. 3^5| 3^6 | A396139..A000244
%C A396541  [3^(n-1)+1..5^(n-1)]| 5^0| 5^1| 5^2| 33.. 5^3| 5^4|  244.. 5^5| 5^6 | A396206..A000351
%C A396541  [5^(n-1)+1..7^(n-1)]| 7^0| 7^1| 7^2|129.. 7^3| 7^4| 3141.. 7^5| 7^6 |        ..A000420
%C A396541 [7^(n-1)+1..11^(n-1)]|11^0|11^1|11^2|346..11^3|11^4|16819..11^5|11^6 | a(n)   ..A001020
